# Shipperbee Delivery - Project Core

## Project Overview
Mobile delivery app for last-mile delivery consolidation. Flutter app with `lib/main_dev.dart` as dev entry point (flavors: Dev, etc.).

## Architecture
- **Layers**: Presentation (ui/), Domain (business logic), Data (network/, models/)
- **State**: Provider for context-based DI; GetIt for non-context services
- **Structure**: Feature-based under `lib/` (ui/, network/, models/, util/)

## Key Conventions
- Entry points: `main_dev.dart`, `main.dart` (set via `Environment.setEnvironment`)
- Use `dart_format` and `analyze_files` for formatting/linting
- Use `logging` package, not `print`
- Explain Dart-specific features (null safety, futures, streams) when suggesting code
